                           libraries
                           
                           worldwide
                           A case study of decision making under pressure, this text covers the Cuban missile crisis. Using the missile crisis as a basic
                              frame of reference, it seeks to teach students how to compare and contrast perspectives on foreign affairs

Nuclear terrorism : the ultimate preventable catastrophe by 
 Graham T Allison(
                              Book
                              )16
                           editions published
                           
                           between
                           2004
                           and
                           2013
                           in 
                           English
                           and held by
